Class ActionReportResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.glassfish.admin.rest.results.Result
      • org.glassfish.admin.rest.results.ActionReportResult

  • public class ActionReportResult
extends Result
    Response information object. Returned on call to GET methods on command resources. Information used by provider to generate the appropriate output.

    Ludovic Champenois
